DOWNFALLU-BEYOND_ARMOR.description:
Gain {Block:diff()} [gold]Block[/gold].
Put {Cards:diff()} random [gold]Offclass[/gold] cards from your [gold]Draw Pile[/gold] into your [gold]Hand[/gold].{InCombat:|
[gold]Gift[/gold]: Common.}

DOWNFALLU-BLUNDERBUS.description:
Deal {Damage:diff()} damage to ALL enemies.
Repeat for every card that costs {Energy:energyIcons()} or more in your [gold]Hand[/gold].{InCombat:
(Repeat {Hits:diff()} additional times)|}

DOWNFALLU-COBRA_COIL.description:
Deal {Damage:diff()} damage.
Enemy takes {ConstrictedPower:diff()} damage at the end of each of its turns.{InCombat:|
[gold]Gift[/gold]: Rare Attack.}

DOWNFALLU-COMBO_STRING.description:
Deal {Damage:diff()} damage for each [gold]Offclass[/gold] card played this turn.{InCombat:|
[gold]Gift[/gold]: Uncommon.}{InCombat:
(Hit {Hits:diff()} times)|}

DOWNFALLU-DANGER_NOODLE.description:
Deal {Damage:diff()} damage.
[gold]Muddle[/gold] a card.{InCombat:|
[gold]Gift[/gold]: Card that cost {Energy:energyIcons()} or more.}

DOWNFALLU-DEFENSIVE_FLAIR.description:
Gain {CalculatedBlock:diff()} [gold]Block[/gold].
Gain {CalculationExtra:diff()} [gold]Block[/gold] for each [gold]Offclass[/gold] card in your [gold]Hand[/gold].{InCombat:|
[gold]Gift[/gold]: Uncommon.}

DOWNFALLU-LUCKY_BREAK.description:
